The Budhi Gandaki Hydroelectric is a proposed [[Hydroelectricity|hydroelectric]] project on the [[Budhi Gandaki River]].  Development by [[Nepal Electricity Authority]]. the extent of the area that will be inundated by the reservoir of the planned 1,200 [[Watt|MW]] project and the place where the people living there will be relocated. The project is expected to displace 45,000 people.<ref>http://www.bghep.gov.np/about-the-project.php</ref><ref>http://kathmandupost.ekantipur.com/news/2016-02-17/land-required-for-budhi-gandaki-project-marked.html</ref>

